{
  "stem": "22004.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So in the meantime, they was-- they was there about a week or two in the-- in the city.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they started coming in close-- the Russians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So finally, the-- the Russians came in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they moved out the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the Russians were maybe about-- about three or four weeks in the city.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then-- then we found out as they started the people to talk are the Russians going to go away, because they got a deal with the-- with the Germans just to go to the River Bug.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it's not far-- the Bug was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when they-- then they started to go back, the Russians, and the Germans came back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we was-- we was in the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were hanging around the city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we lived close in that house-- in that house, not far.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The house was not demolished completely.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were staying around in the meantime.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it was-- was close, that house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in the meantime, the-- the-- the Russians started to move out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we decided to move out too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we took out-- we-- we hired a horse and buggy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- we put it in-- we put it in our-- this-- we got a lot of shoes still.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We took it out from that house and put it in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we went over the Bug.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from there, Siemiatycze-- I don't know if you got it marked down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from Siemiatycze, we-- we took a train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to Lida then Vilnius.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a lot of customers in Lida.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we came there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we was-- we was there a nice couple months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the-- the Russians were there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By train.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
